casebody.data:
No. 10-136. Robert Horel, Warden, Petitioner v. Felix Solorio Valdovinos. 562 U.S. 1196, 131 S. Ct. 1042,

178 L. Ed. 2d 860,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1035, January 24, 2011.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Harrington v. Richter, 562 U.S. 86, 131 S. Ct. 770, 178 L. Ed. 2d 624 (2011).

Same case below, 598 F.3d 568.
